cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ProofGate in research, please cite this software."
title: "ProofGate: a verifiable redaction gateway for hybrid LLM deployment"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-05-04"
license: "Apache-2.0"
abstract: "ProofGate studies and implements a local gateway that projects sensitive inputs into externally visible views for external LLM APIs, with reproducible privacy and utility reports."
keywords:
  - privacy-preserving LLM
  - verifiable redaction
  - data desensitization
  - hybrid LLM deployment
  - tokenization
  - auditability
authors:
  - name: "ProofGate contributors"
